content.detailedDescription: On december 9th around 8:26 pm my wife and i seen what appeared to be a stationary, cluster like formation of blinking lights in the south eastern sky, they then formed into a line and passed over us in a north westerly direction....They blinked and appeared to move in unison, as if they were part of a single craft however we could see stars around and in between, each individual blinking light....This experience was unnerving enough that we called 911, the dispatcher informed me that we were the fifth caller about these lights and they had an officer with a visual as we spoke...The dispatcher also said they were going to make some calls about this and would contact us with any information they learned...We have yet to hear back from them......  it took this line of lights 20 minutes to pass over our location....As they got further away they appeared to resume the cluster like formation which i believe was actually caused by a difference in altitude of the individual objects that couldn't be distinguished while it was overhead.....I observed the distance the line itself covered  and timed a jet the next day to see how long it took the jet to cover the same distance that the line of lights took up in the sky.....It took the jet 1 minute and 45 seconds to cover the same distance that the line of lights took up in the sky.....Based on this, i'm guessing the line itself to be 10+ miles in length.....As they passed over there was no noise at all, we were trying to take pictures and video and were experiencing a lot of trouble with our camera shutting off....We also experienced trouble with our land line telephone when we tried to call 911 the phone went dead and had a constant high pitched mono tone beep that lasted for 4 minutes even after hanging the phone up on the base several times.....The brief footage i was able to capture shows only the part of the line that fit in the cameras view.....From end to end, it stretched over a huge portion of the sky.  i do not believe this to be any sort of man made or operated craft and i believe anyone who seen it would agree with my assumption.  i am willing to undergo a polygraph concerning what i witnessed and would love to hear any further information you may obtain from any other reports on this incident.  i will also send the video footage i was able to get when i'm contacted by an investigator.
content.summary: Line of lights across the sky

content.detailedDescription:
in 1993 corfe mullen, dorset (13 years old) i remember walking home from my friends house, it was 10 o'clock at night and i was meant to be home by 9.
i started to walk home but stopped to look at one silent bright star in the sky, but it wasn't a star. the the light slowly appeared to get bigger and then split in to three stars. 
suddenly i remember looking about and i was raising up above the roof tops! 

then, i was standing in the exact same position, when i looked at my watch it was 12oclock. 2 hours had passed. my watch was working still, but even though i thought i was floating previously, i assumed i was imagining it and went home.

luckily my mum was a sleep but i was able to sneak through the back door.
 
since i was a child, i have always been able to see ghosts, hear and sense them, since i had that experience i have had much weirder experiences, including seeing in to the future.
which quite a few people have experienced first hand from me.

despite my dyslexia and the bipolar, ptsd and anxiety i have developed due to my child hood being disrupted by a violent step dad, i have kept going. 

i have always believed something has been done to me, as i think i have had more children than i have.

i have two girls, one super smart but not so practical, the other very visually creative and logically practical.

both fast learners.

both slightly gifted with future sense.

i'm only 37 and have already started in the direction of menopause. 

i feel like i should have more children. and i love babies, it's like i miss babies. 

i even still lactate which the doctors can't explain as it's been happening since i was 15.

i believe i had a miscarriage at 16, and a confirmed one, one month before i fell pregnant with my eldest.

i fell pregnant again 16 months later.

i've not used the pill contraception or a condom since my eldest was 3 years.

i haven't been pregnant since, but my periods have been long, short, heavy ect every one is different. 

now i have two periods a month or a three week bleed.
content.summary: Saw 3 lights came towards me, next i was above a row of houses, then i was back again.

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving west on a street parallel to hallendale blvd, and ahead of me i was a block away from mardi gras casino. the skies were clear and very blue, nothing else in the sky. for the 5 min i had been driving i hadn’t seen any airplanes. i stopped at a stop sign and i see this silver dot, the sun was reflecting on it which made it appear like an shiny earring in the ocean, you can’t miss it. the object hovered for about a min and since it was a quiet street, no cars, i stayed at the stop sign looking up ahead of me. i wear contacts and my eyes get dry so i was thinking it was a balloon or a weirdly angled airplane but i keep looking at it while blinking to get some moisture to my eyes and the object didn’t move! it just stayed there for about almost another minute until i had to move my car. i looked straight to drive and when i looked back up the object was gone. 
it had a round middle and the wings were rounded as well, different from a pointy wing of an airplane. the sun was reflecting on it so i could definitely see the shape but also the object was far from me, like the size of a round pill. it had a chrome, grey color, really shiny i mean one of my other thoughts was that it was a military aircraft but it couldn’t be because it was chromed out like it was buffed.
long story short this experience leaves me with some questions, i personally do not believe aliens are living with us or are at a higher level of intelligence to the point of flying to our world but i do believe they’re somewhere in this universe that have the same level of intelligence as us, wondering the same thing about aliens, wondering about us as we are about them. 
just saying that i’m skeptical so for me to report this to you guys is big because i tend to have an explaination for things like this. for all i could know it could be a balloon that has kept a certain amount of helium that managed to stay in place for a couple of minutes and then popped when i looked back due to the atmospheric pressure.
content.summary: Driving west, clear blue skies. object looked like airplane but was rounder in shape and hovered for about a min.

content.detailedDescription: I was asleep, and then i could feel something around me and i slowly opened my eyes everything was very blurry and i could see three figures one standing directly over me to looking at a big wall of different colored lights in front of me. as i open my eyes and saw the figure standing above me i felt thrown back and then i was back in my bed. i could not move my body and i looked around the room with my eyes and i tried to open my mouth and call my girlfriend who is laying next to me and the only thing i could make was a small sound and then my eyes shut and i was back asleep and she can confirm that i made a weird noise that night. the next day we saw on the news that there were several unidentified flying objects over lexington county.
content.summary: Like a dream

content.detailedDescription: I was in my house on 12/09/2017 in lexington county sc. at around 7pm when i realized i had forgotten to bring in the mail. when i went outside to get the mail i heard a humming rumbling noise that made me look up, and i seen a long trail of objects. there were triangle  shaped one's that were flashing red and blue lights and in between the triangle shaped objects there were cylinder shaped reddish colored objects flashing a red light on and off.  these object's were in a line one behind the other and they were in this order, a triangle shaped one, then 3 cylinder shaped ones, then another triangle shaped one, and 3 cylinder shaped one's and so on  for a total of around 15 objects or so, they stretched out for a couple miles form what i could tell. it was very clear night and these objects were flying relatively low and not moving very fast so i was able to get a pretty good look at them for about 8 minutes or so . i observed them flying in a straight line until i could not see them anymore because of the trees. the objects stayed at the same altitude the whole time that i could see them  , i live very close to an airport and am very familiar with planes and helicopters flying over my house and i can tell you these were not airplanes or helicopters, i did go on line the next day and had seen a couple other people posted that they had witnessed the same thing i had witnessed with pretty much the same detail that the objects were flying in a straight line and they had seen 10 to 15 objects flashing red and blue lights! my reaction when i seen these objects was complete excitement i could not believe what i was looking at i was not frightened at all it was an awesome sight. since this happened i have been going outside every night at 7pm and looking up at the sky hoping that they will return.
content.summary: 10 to 15 objects triangel shaped and circuler shaped traveling in a line 1 behind another flashing lights low rate of speed

content.detailedDescription:
I noticed the object at approx. 20:40 est while driving home in my car.
it was glowing and flashing bright white light and did not appear to be moving. initially i thought the object was a helicopter but as i observed the object it did not behave like a helicopter.  the object hovered in the sky (high above houses) with its bright white lights.  i sat a stop sign staring at the object trying to figure out what it was and while observing it, its white lights were flashing in a random patterns.  the object would hover, move fast changing direction and then go back to hovering.  i made a left turn onto another street and the object moved in the direction in which i drove. it continued to glow bright white and blinking.  the object changed directions appearing to follow my route home and it continued to glow bright white and blink but as i got closer to my house its colors changed back and forth from white to green to white and randomly blink.  i parked my car and stood in my drive way staring at the object watching it hover over the houses across the street, the object hovered and then it just suddenly disappeared.
content.summary: Object with changing bright lights (white & green)

content.detailedDescription:
I was first of april 2016, i remember the date because at first i thought it was an april fool's. i was on the second floor of my house and was getting ready to go to bed. 
i had just moved towards my curtains which had been open until this point. when i saw an odd light outside, i originally thought it had been because i had my bedroom light on, but i turned the light off and it was still there. my room looked out onto a building site of a nursing home. the light was slightly covered by the corner of the building site which is when the light came round the corner. 
at first i thought it was a pixie or mythical character because i didnt recognise it. it looked rather small from the tall window i was looking through.
the thing was looking around as if it had lost something, and i thought i was dreaming so i knocked on the window, ever so quietly, yet it looked up at me. we stood looking at each other for many moments, with these huge eyes.
i then stepped back from the window, to see if i walked back if it was still there.

i must have stepped back from the window for about a minute, to refresh my mind set when i looked back outside, it wasn't there anymore. so relieved i shut my curtains and turned back to my room and it was on my bed.

my bed was positioned in the middle of the room and my door was shut. i didn't see how it had got into my room but it was standing on my bed. it didn't meet my hips in height but had a very large head and skinny body. 

it was whilst i was starring at it, that it pointed at me and then back to himself/herself. that was when it came over to me but it was walking weirdly as if it had injured itself. 

i was sitting down at this point as i was feeling faint, i dont whether it was the alien's doing or the fact i was seeing something that shouldnt have been real. 

it touched my over my heart, it was so cold i couldnt physically feel the being but i coudl feel the energy, the coldness and then it walked up the wall and through the open window, which had been closed before.
i ran to the window to see two beings walking in the opposite direction than i saw it before, walk through the short hedge and disappear just before crossing the road. completely disappear into thin area.
content.summary: Did not see

content.detailedDescription: I placed my sony video camera on a tripod in my back yard in slacks creek queensland australia around 7.30 am and aimed it at the sun as it rose above the trees beyond my neighbors house.I had the camera angled just above the roof of the neighbors house but left the top of tree in his yard in the picture.I wanted to film the sunrise.I left the camera there filming away for about an hour.When i played the film back i noticed a beautiful beam of light to the left of the sun..It looked like a multi colored parachute and the beam seemed to be coming from a disc shaped object near the sun.The disc shaped object is visible for around 30 seconds and is then covered by clouds although if you zoom in on a still image you can see it behind the clouds for some time.The beam of light stays visible for around eight or nine minutes before it too is covered completely by cloud.The object does not appear to be moving.At first i only noticed the beam of light and i thought it was coming from the sun and maybe reflecting of the clouds but if you follow the v shape of the beam it narrows to a point that directly leads to the disc shaped object.It seems to be projecting out (narrow to wide) from the disc not the sun.Because of the glare of the sun i did not notice anything odd until i played the video back.I just thought it was a beautiful sunrise and worth filming.My partner and i both sat and viewed the video.It looks amazing.
content.summary: Large disc shaped object projecting an enormous parachute like colored beam of light

content.detailedDescription:
It came out of the low clouds right above us 
moved in a straight path for atleast 7 seconds and then disappeared. no sound. my boyfriend was walking toward me and i asked him, did you see that? he said he did but it was more in his peripheral vision. my visual was straight on. i could see detail. it was huge kind of oval shaped. silver smooth surface with some curves, hard to explain but could see the windows all the way around the side that was facing me, rectangle windows and bright white lights. i've always believed in ufos and have witnessed other sightings but this one was more clear than ever even tho it was short. my boyfriend didn't even really believe in them and he didn't deny seeing it. we were in the city residential area. for it to show itself to us there is a little frightening. its been over a year and i still see it like it was yesterday. although i can't remember the exact date. i decided to report it now because i'm watching a documentary on tv and its all about mufon sightings. i figured i might as well report it. still can't get over how big it was. i wish i had a camera or phone pics but happened so fast there was no time. i could try drawing it though. now i see i can attach a drawing or can i send one through email?
content.summary: My boyfriend and i just pulled into the driveway i got out of the car first and was standing by the garage looking back at my boyfriend walking up and couldn't help but see the object come out of the clouds was very low and i could see detail 6-7sec gone

content.detailedDescription: I was with my friend, we were walking to a school nearby to just hang out, and my friend pointed out that there was this blue ball like thing bouncing around in the air, then purple rings went around it then just disappeared, i did not get a video of that. but as we were walking back home, my friend pointed out this fireball looking thing in the sky, so i quickly got my camera out and started filming. then all of a sudden it got really red then it like exploded and a blueish light came out of the ufo and it was like a spotlight coming out of it and it left blue particles in the air as it moved away, it was going pretty slow. i went to look at my camera to watch what i had recorded, and part of my video was deleted and it made the video into 2 separate videos. i lost sight of the ufo when it disappeared.
content.summary: I was with my friend walking , when all of a sudden a fireball looking thing was in the air, then it like exploded and let out light

content.detailedDescription: When i'm outside i always look around to see how many planes i can see in the sky at one time. this particular evening my wife and i went outside to smoke and while looking for planes i noticed what i thought was an incredibly bright star directly over the sunset. i thought it was odd because the sky was still very bright since the sun had just gone below the horizon. i pointed it out to my wife and she thought it was weird too. while we were discussing it we looked around to see if there were any other stars shining back to the east. when we looked back the star was gone. we were both puzzled and wondering where it could have gone and then i noticed that it was all of a sudden way further south and much higher in the sky. the change in distance was way to fast for any modern aircraft known to the general public. i pointed it out to my wife and we were both more perplexed than before. now it appeared to start ascending sightly then appeared to start sinking slowly like a feather and to our amazement it started shimmering out and disappeared. this happened very fast to where it fizzled out and was completely gone within 3 seconds. the way it acted and how bright it was made us think it was a mirror like finish reflecting the sun and then that finish was "shut off" as if there were flaps turning around to stop the reflection.
content.summary: Extremely bright sphere directly over sunset.

content.detailedDescription:
Returning home after dropping my girfriend off at work for a night shift , i parked the car in the drive at 2140 gmt on sunday 10 dec 2017.
with the intention of removing some laundry from the rear passenger seat,i paused for a moment to take in the night sky, only to have my attention taken by something that appeared to be visibly moving through the darkness of the night sky about 50-100 feet above me.
noticeable to me, due to 3, dim, but visible glowing orange rings that outlined a triangular shaped object.
i would say that the object i was viewing from my perspective, was passing over me showing its undercarriage.
the object was not illuminated by any other lights , only by the orange rings as i indicated earlier.
the object appeared to be dark in colour as it was being viewed by myself from the ground and was a dark night sky above.
this said, the outline of the object was visible enough to the naked eye and unmistakeably triangular
the triangular object was moving approximately at around 20-30 mph, silently, with no air movement felt.
travelling west, to an easterly direction the object passed out of my sight over the neighbouring property.
i did run to the main road which was some 20 metres from my viewing position in the drive...To try and capture an image.
however a combination of the time to set the camera on my fone,and trying to pinpoint object in a now brightly lit street, ended the encounter with only my account as documented here.
i feel personally as though i have encountered something remarkable ....
having had several other undocumented encounters i felt compelled to try and find a medium to have this recorded.
the local police force has a documented account of my observation of this object.
whether there may be any future dealings with the authoritys i dont know...But am only to willing to share this experience with those who are interested or may have more details to put my way as too what i saw on this evening.
content.summary: Craft moving silently, clearing trees and buildings,triangular shaped object, illuminated visible rings

content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Shiny orb like object

content.detailedDescription: I was on my way home from work.The time was about 6:15 pm.Traffic heading towards vancouver was heavier than normal.Something in the distance up in the sky caught my eye.It was a string of lights that appeared to be very close together.They were blue,red,white.They gave the appearance of belonging to one unit.They seemed to close together to be separate planes - especially given the fact that these were flying right over vancouver air space.Vancouver has a huge amount of air traffic through this area constantly.The description was exactly the same as given recently for the denver lights - supposed military convoy (over vancouver airspace in british columbia canada?).Due to a curve in the road and heavy traffic heading towards vancouver i did lose sight of the event.I would have pulled over had there been a safe place to do so. i could not tell if it was hovering or not.My only feeling upon seeing the object was that it seemed to be one object with a string of lights.
content.summary: While driving home from work i saw a string of red blue and white lights they appeared to be very close together they seemed lower than the surrounding mountains - same exact description as denver lights

content.detailedDescription:
1. so, in order for this to make more sense, a few nights before seeing the ufo, i had a "dream" or "abduction." i was pregnant and met with one plaeidian woman, with greys behind her.

1b. i was at my mom's house when i saw the ufo. i was out front looking at the sky, 

2.And noticed a strange blinking that didn't match any other aerial craft pattern.

4. the object had this eerie blue/green glow to it, just hanging out in the air. (i live semi-near an airport so air traffic is busy) so an airplane was flying towards it (plane going west), and the ufo started to fly towards the plane. it looked like they were about to collide, but then the ufo sorta just 'blipped' from sight. like, it just disappeared, and the airplane just kept flying west. about 10 seconds later, i see the ufo show up, and glitch into the shape of a plane (still going opposite direction of the real plane).

5. to me, it felt like validation of the "abduction" experience i had a couple days prior. i felt like, they knew i was observing them. i felt at ease, and energized. sorta like how a little girl feels when she gets ice cream.

6. it kept flying east, and eventually faded out from my view; but the strange part was that it didnt have any flashing lights after transmogging into a plane. like, it just had weird looking "headlights" but no flashing on where plane wings would've been.
content.summary: I was pregnant, had a "dream" met aliens. days later see "airplane" in the sky. changed shape from ufo to plane.

content.detailedDescription:
It was after dinner time as i was sitting on the couch watching tv and by chance i looked out of my first floor  window(big window)  to see two flashing objects in the sky. 

there is some construction space next to the place of residence,  a park and more buildings . the two flashing lights were hovering above this space and then disappeared behind the buildings after about 10 seconds. my mother joked it was ufos. i didn't take her seriously.

less than15 seconds later i see three more lights just floating and moving one behind the other. they eventually take like a turn and  disappear behind the building.

i was initially creeped out as no one else seemed to notice this and the streets and parks were quite active. then eventually i just wanted it to come back so i could find out what it was. i also researched to see if there are any scientific labs near my residence (to find another explanation) but didnt succeeded.
content.summary: Sitting in my mothers  first floor apartment, i noticed flashing lights right outside the window in the sky. first there were two ,then they disappeared. this was followed by three other lights all flying in the same direction, like follow the leader.

content.detailedDescription: Me and a friend were on our way home from a concert, the females were sleeping in back, we were driving aprox 90 from nashville to lexington, ky. no drugs, no alcohol at concert. we just crossed the kentucky state line when we came across 3 vehicles stopped on sode of road, and above the vehicles aprox 100 feet in front of them, a good 60 feet in the air was a very prominent object hovering, no visible lights, but visible to us, it was transparent, but only enough to make you double take, transparent as casper, in the priginal film. we couldnt hear noise where we were. as we watched this item, for a good minute, we tried to snap a photo, using a note 8 and a iphone and were unable to actually capture anything die to lighting, and being on interstate at 4 am. as we decided we were spooked enough, we decided to continue forward, along with another vehicle that was parked on side. as we approach the object, which hasnt made any movement besides the swaying of hovering, we hesr this loud, harsh humming, and again, we just left a concert, we are deaf temporarily, so this noise had to be loud. it rumbled and just sucked in all. we didnt feel any effects from the encounter, we even stopped a few miles up the road at a gas station to verify what we did see, the other car stopped with us to talk about the experience. we lost site driving away, and never turned around.
content.summary: It was hovering above a creek, 3 vehicles witnessed

content.detailedDescription:
I was getting ready for bed when i heard unusually loud helicopter flying by my home. i went outside to observe. from my back deck, i continued to hear the loud sound of what i assumed was a low flying helicopter and observed lights that i assumed were from the helicopter. i then saw 2 lights in front of the helicopter.
 the 2 lights  appeared to be about 75 feet in front of the helicopter and maybe slightly lower than the helicopter. the 2 lights were separated  from each other by a distance equal to or slightly greater  than the size of the helicopter. the 2 lights were steady, unblinking and slightly smaller than the helicopter lights. the two lights did not appear at all like the helicopter lights. 
 the helicopter and 2 lights were traveling south to north. they were not directly over head but at approximately 30 degrees above the horizon. the distance was approximately 1/4 mile. 
the incident happened while dark and on a clear night. because the observation time was so brief (maybe 15 seconds) and the lights so low, i was not able to determine if the two lights were connected to each other or if they were independent of each other. i lost of of the lights due to trees and neighborhood homes.
it is not unusual that a helicopter would fly near my home. what was unusual was the low altitude and the noise. the altitude was very low and the helicopter sound was very loud. i suspect it was a very large helicopter. and of course, it was very strange to see two unidentifiable lights moving in front of the helicopter. 
i did not have any unusual or altered feelings during or after the sighting.
content.summary: At night, i saw  2 lights, the size of airplane lights, traveling in front of helicopter.

content.detailedDescription: I was standing at the back door talking to my daughter on the phone when i saw about 7 to 9 bright red fireball looking lights in the sky. at first i thought maybe its military helicopters going to the rifle, colorado airport but there was no sound & they were flying too close together. a couple of the red light seemed to be to the left but, most were in a straight line traveling to the west over the mountains. i woke my husband up to come see & he caught sight of them towards the end before they went over the mountain tops & he thought they were strange as well.
content.summary: Red lights in the sky
